1
00:00:42,720 --> 00:00:44,160
Tiandao Palace

2
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:47,400
plans to permanently seal the Netherworld,

3
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:49,600
so that the human world

4
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,960
will no longer be

5
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,610
troubled by Nether Demons.

6
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:54,080
However,

7
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,720
we need your contribution.

8
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:58,360
Are you willing,

9
00:00:58,480 --> 00:00:59,640
Lanqi Moyuan?

10
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:06,200
Does the contribution you speak of, Palace Master,

11
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,800
require Moyuan's life?

12
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,480
Not your life.

13
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:14,560
It just requires you

14
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,360
to willingly

15
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,240
sacrifice

16
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:20,520
the blood of the Likong Clan within you

17
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,920
to complete the formation.

18
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,260
Palace Master,

19
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,740
does the human blood in Moyuan's body

20
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:33,160
truly come from the Likong Clan?

21
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,200
But

22
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,960
Moyuan has never felt

23
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,330
any similarity to them.

24
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:41,009
You don't need to overthink it.

25
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,160
You just need

26
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:45,440
to separate the human blood from your body

27
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,520
and when the formation takes shape,

28
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,160
inject it in time.

29
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:54,340
Palace Master,

30
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,960
forcibly extracting human blood

31
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:59,640
is like burning one's soul in a sacrificial fire.

32
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,280
Moyuan...

33
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:03,800
If you can help the human race seal the Netherworld,

34
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,600
then Li Junbai

35
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:08,280
will have done a great deed for the human race,

36
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,919
and can live out his days in peace.

37
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,440
Otherwise,

38
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:15,280
with his identity as a Likong Clan member,

39
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:17,240
I'm sure you know

40
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,760
what his fate will be.

41
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,160
I, Moyuan,

42
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,720
am willing to use my life as the foundation,

43
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:48,210
to completely isolate the Human Realm

44
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,620
from the Netherworld.

45
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:58,810
Palace Lord.

46
00:02:59,079 --> 00:03:00,720
The array is almost ready.

47
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,080
The Likong clansmen have been bled.

48
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,480
We await your command.

49
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:05,960
Very good.

50
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,320
Go.

51
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:11,090
Let the ceremony begin.

52
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,120
Wait, wait.

53
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:13,560
Wait.

54
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,780
Palace Master.

55
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,400
Although Lanqi Moyuan is a half-human, half-demon,

56
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,530
for all these years,

57
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:22,160
he has worked hard without complaint.

58
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:22,690
Even when

59
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,760
covered in wounds,

60
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:26,760
he has suppressed the Netherworld for the human race.

61
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,920
He has made contributions

62
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:29,240
and worked hard.

63
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,800
I implore you, Palace Master,

64
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:33,079
to let Lanqi Moyuan stay in Lanqi.

65
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,079
I, Junbai,

66
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,920
am willing to join him forever

67
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,040
for the human race

68
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:39,180
to suppress the Netherworld.

69
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:41,200
Grandpa!

70
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,800
Since you want to help him suppress it,

71
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:47,040
do it together.

72
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:49,280
Thank you, Palace Master.

73
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,940
Palace Master.

74
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,120
Yuan,

75
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,360
live well.

76
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,800
Yuan.

77
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,600
Yuan.

78
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,680
Everyone,

79
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:36,200
it's all my fault.

80
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,520
Wait, wait.

81
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,040
Wait.

82
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,760
Yuan.

83
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:44,080
Live well.

84
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:48,120
Grandpa.

85
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,240
Why?

86
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:57,159
Why do you have to be sacrificed too, Grandpa?

87
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,560
Grandpa did it for the human race.

88
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,360
Sacrificing oneself,

89
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,240
and giving one's all.

90
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:00,520
So,

91
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:03,280
how dare a mere Likong defy my decision.

92
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,650
Everything my Tiandao Palace does

93
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:08,740
is for the eternal foundation of the human race.

94
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:12,160
It is also an everlasting blessing for humanity.

95
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,880
Does a lowly Likong

96
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,320
deserve to speak to me?

97
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,480
Taishu Yi,

98
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:23,360
I will take you down with me.

99
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,200
Everyone, get in position.

100
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,460
Demon-Refining Lock!

101
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,140
Palace Master.

102
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,840
I didn't expect Lanqi Moyuan

103
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,680
to be so terrifying when he goes berserk.

104
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:24,000
I'm afraid the magical artifacts and source blood we prepared

105
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,530
won't be enough to seal him.

106
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,280
Then add more.

107
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,280
But

108
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:33,080
we don't have many Likong clansmen left.

109
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,840
Offer the ones from

110
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,680
the Nursery Pavilion as well.

111
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,200
This...

112
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,100
Go quickly.

113
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,360
Yes.

114
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,320
Let me go.

115
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:52,400
No.

116
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:53,720
Let me go.

117
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,180
It's already full this month.

118
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:57,320
Let me go.

119
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,280
Save us.

120
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,980
Please stop draining.

121
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,480
I'll die if you continue.

122
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,500
Palace Master.

123
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:04,740
Palace Master.

124
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:07,320
Save us, Palace Master.

125
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,080
Let go of me!

126
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,800
Save us!

127
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,560
I have given blood once.

128
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:14,200
I'm willing to give more each time.

129
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,120
Don't kill me.

130
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,280
Stop!

131
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:22,940
Let go of me.

132
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,280
Stop draining it.

133
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:25,160
I'll die if you take more.

134
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,000
Somebody save me!

135
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,000
No.

136
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,640
Stop draining it.

137
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,280
I'll die if you take more.

138
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,299
Palace Master.

139
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,500
Palace Master.

140
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,919
Save us!

141
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:38,720
Palace Master.
